flowchart TD
    subgraph Client [Client Tier: Browser]
        UI[React 19.2 + TailwindCSS]
    end

    subgraph App [Application Tier: Hostinger VPS]
        Nginx[Nginx Proxy]
        subgraph Next [Next.js 16.1]
            Auth[Auth Module]
            Notes[Notes Module]
            Mod[Moderation Module]
            AI[AI Module]
        end
        Nginx --> Next
    end

    subgraph Data [Data & External Services]
        DB[(Neon PostgreSQL)]
        CDN[Cloudinary]
        OAuth[Google OAuth]
        Email[Brevo Email]
        LLM[Gemini 2.5 Flash]
    end

    %% Flow
    Client -->|HTTPS| Nginx
    
    Auth <-->|OAuth 2.0| OAuth
    Auth -->|Drizzle ORM| DB
    
    Notes -->|Drizzle ORM| DB
    Notes -->|Signed Preset| CDN
    Client -.->|Direct Upload & Delivery| CDN
    
    Mod -->|Send Emails| Email
    
    AI <-->|JSON Objects| LLM
    AI -->|Drizzle ORM| DB
